Another example of the ISM not being the best indicator for predicting BTC price action:

Jan 2019:

ISM: 55.7
BTC: $3700

June 2019:

ISM: 51.3
BTC: $13,900

So in this case the ISM dropped over 6 months and the price of BTC went up 4x.
